# Temporary/Placeholder Content Rules üõ†Ô∏è
- All placeholder content must be marked with a standardized comment tag
- Use the format `/* @PLACEHOLDER - Description of what needs to be replaced */`
- For JSX/TSX inline comments use `{/* @PLACEHOLDER - Description */}`
- For HTML use `<!-- @PLACEHOLDER - Description -->`
- For CSS use `/* @PLACEHOLDER - Description */`
- All placeholder comments must include a brief description of what should replace it
- Never ship code to production with @PLACEHOLDER tags remaining